00:39:26.800 --> 00:39:29.120
But Lady La-ong Dao holds a higher status, honey.

00:39:29.440 --> 00:39:32.440
But Lady Lek is prettier.

00:39:32.440 --> 00:39:35.160
But Lady La-ong Dao is the daughter of Lord Anirut, honey.

00:39:35.560 --> 00:39:38.120
Father. Mother. Please stop.

00:39:39.280 --> 00:39:41.760
Is this a welcome back party…

