Yes, Rueduee is absolutely right.

00:41:51.840 --> 00:41:54.440
I often saw men dance together back when I was still abroad.

00:42:00.840 --> 00:42:01.640
Kaew.

00:42:04.120 --> 00:42:05.360
Please dance with me.

00:42:16.520 --> 00:42:17.720
Please, Kaew.

00:42:17.720 --> 00:42:21.640
None of us here can help him right now except you.

00:42:21.640 --> 00:42:23.240
Please help him.

